shape: sequence_diagram

b: Browser
hp: "NSC HTTP proxy\n127.0.0.1:8080"
r: NscRouter
gw: NSGW
nsn: NSN

b -> hp: CONNECT ssh.office.n.ns:22 HTTP/1.1
hp -> hp: 读 headers，丢到空行
hp -> r: "lookup_domain(\"ssh.office.n.ns\") → site=office"
hp -> gw: "WSS + CMD_OPEN_V4 (ssh.office.n.ns:22, TCP)\n(NscRouter.open_stream)"
gw -> nsn: relay (stream_id 映射)
nsn -> gw: OpenAck
gw -> hp: OpenAck
hp -> b: "HTTP/1.1 200 Connection established\\r\\n\\r\\n"
note: 双向透传(copy_bidirectional),本代理无状态
